review_blob: xmas version of the Grabanc, but not the typical overspiced xmas brew... beautiful reddish color, not too light, not too heavy: really refreshing!

draught at Csakajsrk, Budapest, Hungary // fell in love with this hazy, not disturbingly sweet double IPA; just what I needed after a killer week! the bitterness in the end doesnt let you go easily, but you dont want to be let gone anyway...
beer_name: To l Dangerously Close to Stupid
